data.title: Lady Elizabeth Brooke Warner (1503
data.meta_description: Daughter of Thomas Brooke, 8th Lord Cobham & Dorothy Heydon.  She married Sir Thomas Wyatt in 1520.    Elizabeth Brooke was the wife of Thomas Wyatt, the poet, and the mother of Thomas Wyatt the younger who led Wyatt's Rebellion against Mary I. She was the sister of George Brooke, 9th Baron Cobham (Memorial# 34917975)...
